to.shell_command:
osascript -e 'set appName to "Emacs"
set startIt to false
tell application "System Events"
  if not (exists process appName) then
    set startIt to true
  else
    set frontmost of process appName to true
  end if
end tell
if startIt then
  tell application appName to activate
end if'
